&lt;p&gt;업무내용&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>첫월급</title><link>https://yshghid.github.io/docs/hobby/daily/daily57/</link><pubDate>Thu, 07 May 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://yshghid.github.io/docs/hobby/daily/daily57/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="첫월급"&gt;
 첫월급
 &lt;a class="anchor" href="#%ec%b2%ab%ec%9b%94%ea%b8%89"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;#2026-05-07&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;p&gt;첫월급으로 골라본 엄마아빠 선물 ㅎㅎ&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img width="2654" height="1918" alt="image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/89e61fad-3f26-49a2-b3c0-57178bb17648" /&gt;
&lt;img width="2640" height="1912" alt="image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/b70bc105-e76a-496d-8468-0651f04b1342" /&gt;
&lt;p&gt;엄마는 샤넬 립밤, 아빠는 오쏘몰을 샀다.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;배송 늦을까봐 일치감치 결제했는데 엄마껀 5.7, 아빠꺼는 5.8 배송 예정이다 ㅎㅎ&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=""&gt;
 
 &lt;a class="anchor" href="#"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;img width="1658" height="1158" alt="image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/3aaf7898-3e90-4032-a8d8-e7f4b8366357" /&gt;
&lt;p&gt;25년 종소세신고했는데 81마넌이나 환급!!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=""&gt;
 
 &lt;a class="anchor" href="#"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;img width="2594" height="1104" alt="image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/7ee7a7ac-b67e-46f2-b2c0-f38743d05245" /&gt;
&lt;p&gt;그리고 청년내일저축을 신청했다.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;매달 10마넌만 납입하면 되긴 한데 3년동안 &amp;lsquo;근속&amp;rsquo;하면서 납입해야해서 요기 오래다녀야한다&amp;hellip; ㅎㅎ (아니면 환승이직하거나 ㅋㅋㅎㅎ)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=""&gt;
 
 &lt;a class="anchor" href="#"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;그리고 저축은 고민을 좀 해봤는데&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;일단 이번달은 200만원을 저축에 넣었고, 현금도 있고 해서 이번달 생활비는 더 빼서쓰지않아도 될거같다.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;세금환급은 6월에 들어오긴한데 자기 선물 or 커플템 사기 + 5월말에 여행가기 &amp;laquo; 에 다 쓸것같다.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;그리고 다음달부터는 150만원씩 저축하는게 적당할것같다.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;</description></item><item><title>Champagne Supernova</title><link>https://yshghid.github.io/docs/hobby/book/book61/</link><pubDate>Mon, 04 May 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://yshghid.github.io/docs/hobby/book/book61/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="champagne-supernova"&gt;
 Champagne Supernova
 &lt;a class="anchor" href="#champagne-supernova"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;#2026-05-04&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;p&gt;How many special people change?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;얼마나 많은 특별한 사람들이 변할까?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;How many lives are living strange?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;얼마나 많은 사람들이 이상한 삶을 살까?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Where were you while we were getting high?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;넌 어디 있었니, 우리가 취해 있을 때?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Slowly walking down the hall&lt;/p&gt;
